    <lb n="1"/><g type="stauros"/> νομίζω ὅτι εἰ μὴ ἡ χεὶρ τοῦ θεοῦ βοηθήσῃ, τὸ τῆς παροιμίας εἰς ἐμὲ ἔχετε 

    <lb n="2"/>πληρῶσαι ὅτι ἀπῆλθες ἐκ τῆς ὄψεως, ἀπῆλθες <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">καὶ</del> ἐκ τῆς ψυχῆς· ἀπέκαμον γὰρ 

    <lb n="3"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γράφ</supplied>ων ὑμῖν ἵνα διὰ τῶν ἀντιγραφῶν σημά<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied>ατέ μοι <choice><corr>εἰ</corr><sic>εαν</sic></choice> προσέχουσιν <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">η</del> ὑμῖν καὶ 

    <lb n="4"/>ποιοῦσιν ὑμῖν ἀποκρίσεις, καὶ ἀνέμους ἀντιγράφετε μήτε πόδια <choice><corr>ἔχοντος</corr><sic>εχοντ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable"><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>ι</del></sic></choice> μήτε 

    <lb n="5"/>κεφαλὴν. οὐ μὴν ἀλλὰ καὶ Κολλούθου τοῦ παιδὸς πεμφθέντος παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ ἐν τῷ 

    <lb n="6"/>Ἀρσινο<hi rend="diaeresis">ί</hi>τῃ ἔγραψα ὑμῖν πέμψαι τὸ ἐρεοῦν μαλλωτὸν μετὰ καὶ τῶν ἄλλων εἰδῶν 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ διὰ τῆς χάριτος τοῦ θεοῦ τρεῖς ἥμισυ <num value="3  1/2 "/> μῆνας ἐποίησεν ἐκεῖ καὶ ἦλθεν κουφό-

    <lb n="8"/><choice><corr>χερα</corr><sic>κουφαχαιρα</sic></choice> μήτε γράμματα ὑμῶν ἐνεγκών μοι. καὶ ἐν ὅσῳ ταῦτά εἰσιν, ὤφελον 

    <lb n="9"/>καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγὼ</corr><sic>καγω</sic></choice> σχεῖν ἐγκέφαλον καὶ μὴ γράψαι ὑμῖν· καὶ ἀρκεῖ <choice><corr>μοι</corr><sic>μου</sic></choice> ἕως τοῦτο γράψαι. <g type="stauros"/> 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="10"/><g type="stauros"/> σὺν <expan>θ<ex cert="high">εῷ</ex></expan> τῇ <expan>δεσποί<ex cert="high">νῃ</ex></expan> μου  <expan>Φιλοστοργ<ex cert="high">ίᾳ</ex></expan> <expan>μητρ<ex cert="high">ὶ</ex></expan> <g type="stauros"/> Σχολαστικίος <expan>υἱὸ<ex cert="high">ς</ex></expan> <expan>αὐτ<ex cert="high">ῆς</ex></expan>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.17954" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.17954" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0566" type="textDate">vor 566</date></p></div><div n="meta.17954" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. BL IX, S. 226.</p></div><div n="meta.17954" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Ross. Georg.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">12</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">17954</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0197</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">12</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0197;3;12" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.17954" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">226</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.17954" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.17954" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="histo